data.description: All Brick home, corner lot on dead end street!Spacious home offers vaulted large living with FP. Kitchen/Dining w/breakfast bar and   access to the garage for ease of carry in groceries. Patio doors to back covered patio that leads to very large back yard with privacy fence, flower gardens and storage shed. Master suite with walkin closet and full bath. 2 additional bedrooms and full hall bath. Utility at end of hallway with room for desk/storage. 3 car garage offers ALOT of space and attic stairs for storage. Home has all Anderson windows and patio door. Sump pump under home with access in garage and nice gravel under home. Sidewalk along home from garage on front and back, roomy front yard and 2 large spaces on the sides. Great location in town yet off the beaten path!
